Taylor Swift Offers Chance to be on Her Instagram If You Vote|http://www.elle.com|http://www.elle.com/culture/celebrities/a23940538/taylor-swift-vote-instagram-story-feature/||2018-10-19|Alyssa Bailey||Taylor Swift, with her 112 million followers, remains steadfast in her newfound commitment to get people out to vote in the midterm election. Her latest offer: a spot on her Instagram story if you vote, post about it with the #justvoted hashtag, and tag her @taylorswift. She posted the instructions on her Instagram Story just now, so the chance to be featured is open to early voters too.

